## 📊 **PICLAW APP - ARCHITECTURE ANALYSIS**

### 🏗️ **Overall Architecture**

Piclaw is an **AI Coding Assistant** built on top of `@mariozechner/pi-coding-agent`. It provides:
- Interactive TUI mode for chatting with AI
- 140+ custom system tools (sub-tools)
- Custom providers (Kilo, model registry)
- Todo list management
- Memory tool for persistent storage
- Command history persistence
- Context logging for debugging

---

### 📁 **Project Structure**

```
piclaw/
├── src/
│   ├── main.ts              # Entry point (core bootstrap)
│   ├── cli.ts              # CLI wrapper
│   ├── helpers.ts          # Helper functions (API validation, extension registration)
│   ├── piclaw-core.ts     # Core boot logic
│   ├── context-logger.ts  # Debug logging (LLM context)
│   ├── interactive-runner.ts  # TUI runner
│   ├── command-history-patch.ts  # Persistent history
│   ├── migrations.ts     # Config migrations
│   │
│   ├── cli/
│   │   └── args.ts       # CLI argument parser
│   │
│   ├── config/
│   │   ├── config.ts    # Paths & package detection (~/.piclaw)
│   │   └── config-manager.ts  # Persistent config (~/.piclaw/config.json)
│   │
│   ├── services/
│   │   └── command-history.ts  # History service
│   │
│   ├── extensions/       # Custom extensions
│   │   ├── index.ts    # Extension entry point
│   │   ├── auto-memory.ts  # Auto-memory integration
│   │   ├── piclaw-extension.ts
│   │   ├── providers/  # Custom LLM providers
│   │   │   ├── kilo-provider.ts
│   │   │   ├── registry.ts
│   │   │   └── models/
│   │   └── tools/     # Custom tools
│   │       ├── todos-tool.ts   # Todo management (25KB!)
│   │       ├── memory-tool.ts # Memory storage (9KB)
│   │       ├── echo-tool.ts
│   │       └── system-info-tool.ts
│   │
│   ├── tools/
│   │   ├── subtool-loader.ts  # Unified tool (core + 140+ sub-tools)
│   │   └── sub-tools/      # 140+ system tools
│   │       ├── git.ts, docker.ts, k8s.ts
